						<div class="postbody">Just calling it &quot;four_count,&quot; are you sure you'll know what that is if you come back to it in a couple of years?  I would call it something INX_4X to make it more clear what it's doing, and then if you want to tell the reason or significance, put that in the comment to the right.</div>

					
